<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>社媒自动化助手</h1>
            <p>让小企业社媒运营自动化，每天只需5分钟，获取更多客户</p>
            <div class="header-actions">
                <a href="/auth/login" class="btn-outline">登录</a>
                <a href="/auth/register" class="btn-primary">免费试用 7天</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="features" id="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>为什么选择我们？</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon">&#x1F4E4;</div>
                    <h3>自动发布</h3>
                    <p>一键排发朋友圈、微博、抖音等平台内容，定时自动发布</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon">&#x1F916;</div>
                    <h3>智能文案</h3>
                    <p>AI生成营销文案，提升转化率</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon">&#x1F4CA;</div>
                    <h3>数据报表</h3>
                    <p>实时监控曝光、互动，优化运营策略</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing" id="pricing">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>简单定价</h2>
            <div class="price-card">
                <div class="price-badge">最受欢迎</div>
                <h3>专业版</h3>
                <p class="price">&#165;100<small>/月</small></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>&#10003; 无限自动发布</li>
                    <li>&#10003; AI文案生成</li>
                    <li>&#10003; 数据分析报表</li>
                    <li>&#10003; 7x12客服支持</li>
                    <li>&#10003; 多平台管理</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/auth/register" class="btn-primary">立即订阅</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="signup" class="cta">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>准备好提升社媒效果了吗？</h2>
            <p>免费试用7天，无需信用卡，随时取消</p>
            <a href="/auth/register" class="btn-primary btn-large">开始免费试用</a>
            <p class="note">已有 2,345+ 家小企业在使用</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2026 社媒自动化助手. 保留所有权利。</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
